title: 2013–14 Kent Invicta Football League
text:
The 2013–14 Kent Invicta Football League season was the third in the history of the <a href="Kent%20Invicta%20Football%20League">Kent Invicta Football League</a>, a <a href="association%20football">football</a> competition in England.
